{
  "stem": "10572.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I realized that this was a responsibility that if I would fail in this mission, I would have a tough time to live the rest of my life.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I-- I somehow hoped and prayed that I would get my message across.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when the elevator door opened, here was this-- you know, we Europeans had-- had these certain concepts of Americans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they all looked like Marlene Dietrich and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And here was this kind of heavyset woman standing there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I apologized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Introduced my sister and my brother-in-law and apologized for this peculiar way that I asked for this appointment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she looked at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she said, we have been long enough in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I know how things are for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And you have my sympathy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then we-- she asked us to go into the reading room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We went into the reading room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Like many of the elegant hotels would have, all the papers of the world hanging there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And-- and then I looked around to see if we were alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And she picked up on that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And she said, you know, we have been long enough in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I understand this look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "If you feel uncomfortable here, we can go to my room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "This is fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we sat down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I somehow had the feeling, by sizing her up, that she was a kind of straightforward, no small talk, let's get down and talk tachlis.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- although I'm sure she didn't know what tachlis was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She-- I said to her--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When she said, what can I do for you, I said I feel that we have reached the point where we have tried for years and years to see if we could survive here.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
